"Map your model weight directory into the container (the example maps it to "
"`/root/.cache/`)."
msgstr "将模型权重目录映射到容器中（示例映射到`/root/.cache/`）。"

msgid ""
"Save the script as `minimax-docker-run.sh`, then start and enter the "
"container:"
msgstr "将脚本保存为`minimax-docker-run.sh`，然后启动并进入容器："

