msgstr "预期结果：`docker ps`显示容器状态为\"Up\"，`npu-smi info`列出预期的NPU设备数量。"

msgid ""
"If you prefer to build from source instead of using the Docker image, "
"install vLLM-Ascend following the [Installation "
