"In this tutorial, we assume you have downloaded the model weights. Replace "
"`/path/to/weight/` with your actual model weight path."
msgstr "在本教程中，我们假设您已下载模型权重。请将`/path/to/weight/`替换为实际的模型权重路径。"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment completes both Prefill and Decode within the same "
"node, suitable for development, testing, and low-to-medium throughput "
"production scenarios."
msgstr "单节点部署在同一节点内完成Prefill和Decode阶段，适用于开发、测试以及中低吞吐量的生产场景。"

msgid ""
"**Common Issues Tip:** If you encounter OOM, HCCL port conflicts, or other "
"startup issues, please refer to the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) for "
"troubleshooting. For MiniMax-specific issues, refer to [Chapter 10 "
"FAQ](#10-faq)."
msgstr ""
"**常见问题提示：** "
"如果遇到OOM、HCCL端口冲突或其他启动问题，请参考[公共FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html)进行排查。MiniMax相关问题请参考[第10章FAQ](#10-faq)。"

msgid ""
"Below is a recommended startup configuration for short-context conditions "
"(e.g., 3.5k input / 1.5k output) to achieve good performance."
msgstr "以下是短上下文场景（如3.5k输入/1.5k输出）的推荐启动配置，以获得良好性能。"

msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "注意："

msgid "Remarks:"
msgstr "说明："

msgid ""
"PD (Prefill-Decode) separation splits the Prefill and Decode phases across "
"different nodes for better throughput. The following 1P1D configuration is "
"validated for 128k input/output scenarios with `MiniMax-M2.7-W8A8`."
msgstr ""
"PD（Prefill-"
"Decode）分离将Prefill和Decode阶段分散到不同节点上，以获得更好的吞吐量。以下1P1D配置已在`MiniMax-M2.7-W8A8`的128k输入/输出场景中验证。"

msgid ""
"**Hardware**: 2× Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16), one for Prefill, one for Decode."
msgstr "**硬件**: 2× Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16)，一台用于Prefill，一台用于Decode。"

msgid ""
"**Common Issues Tip:** For PD separation specific issues such as KV transfer"
" timeouts or Mooncake connection errors, please refer to the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html). For MiniMax-"
"specific PD separation issues, refer to [Chapter 10 FAQ](#10-faq)."
msgstr ""
"**常见问题提示:** "
"对于PD分离的特定问题，如KV传输超时或Mooncake连接错误，请参考[公共FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html)。对于MiniMax特定的PD分离问题，请参考[第10章FAQ](#10-faq)。"

msgid "First, prepare `launch_online_dp.py` on each node:"
msgstr "首先，在每个节点上准备`launch_online_dp.py`："

msgid "Then prepare `run_dp_template.sh` on each node."
msgstr "然后在每个节点上准备`run_dp_template.sh`。"

msgid "**Prefill node** (set `nic_name` and `local_ip` to your own):"
msgstr "**Prefill节点**（将`nic_name`和`local_ip`设置为自己的）："

msgid "**Decode node** (set `nic_name` and `local_ip` to your own):"
msgstr "**Decode节点**（将`nic_name`和`local_ip`设置为自己的）："

msgid "Once the scripts are ready, start the servers on each node."
msgstr "脚本准备好后，在每个节点上启动服务器。"

msgid "**Prefill node:**"
msgstr "**Prefill节点:**"

msgid "**Decode node:**"
msgstr "**Decode节点:**"

msgid ""
"Run the proxy on any machine that can reach both nodes. You can get the "
"proxy script from the repository: "
"[load_balance_proxy_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)."
msgstr ""
"在任意一台能访问两个节点的机器上运行代理。你可以从仓库获取代理脚本：[load_balance_proxy_server_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)。"

msgid "The service is then accessible at `http://<proxy_ip>:8009`."
msgstr "然后服务可通过`http://<proxy_ip>:8009`访问。"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with input prompts."
msgstr "服务器启动后，你可以使用输入提示查询模型。"

msgid "**Note:**"
msgstr "**注意:**"

msgid ""
"Expected result: HTTP 200 with a JSON response containing a `choices` field "
"with the model's reply text."
msgstr "预期结果：HTTP 200，返回JSON响应，包含`choices`字段，其中包含模型的回复文本。"

msgid ""
"Expected result: The response should contain a coherent self-introduction "
"and tool call parameter format in the `content` field."
msgstr "预期结果：响应应在`content`字段中包含连贯的自我介绍和工具调用参数格式。"

msgid ""
"Expected result: HTTP 200 with a JSON response containing a `tool_calls` "
"field with the function name and arguments."
msgstr "预期结果：HTTP 200，返回JSON响应，包含`tool_calls`字段，其中包含函数名和参数。"

